#Issue Tracker

## Issue tracker project made up of frontend and backend technologies like, EJS, CSS, JAVASCRIPT, NodeJS, ExpressJS, MongoDB, is a application where you can create/add project and further if any issue related to the project then you can also create/add/label issue/issues to it.

- TECHNOLOGIES

* FRONTEND
  > EJS (HTML)
  > CSS
  > JAVASCRIPT
* BACKEND
  > NODEJS
  > EXPRESSJS
  > MONGODB

- ROUTES

 * PROJECTS
 
  > Home page route
  > router.get("/home");
  
  > Issue form page route
  > router.get("/:projectId/issue/form");
  
  > Project form page route
  > router.get("/form");
  
  > Single project details route
  > router.get("/:projectId");
  
  > Project creation route
  > router.post("/create");
  
  > elete Single Project
  > router.post("/:projectId/delete");
  
  > Route for page issue form
  > router.get("/:projectId/issue_form");
  
  > Router for Search Issues
  > router.get("/:projectId/search");
  
  > Router for Filter Issues
  > router.get("/:projectId/filter");
 
 * ISSUES
 
  > Create an issue
  > router.post("/:projectId/issue/create");
